    Direct (limma)

    design<-cbind(Grp1=1, Grp2vs1=smallG_SE$ALL.AML)
fit<-lmFit(assay(smallG_SE), design)
fit<-eBayes(fit) #  Moderated t-statistic
SE_topDE_limma<-topTable(fit, coef=2, number = top_DE_analytes_present)
